<i>the world's first digital quartz...</i>

257
00:16:22,581 --> 00:16:23,878
<i>... liquid crystal chronograph.</i>

258
00:16:24,049 --> 00:16:25,641
<i>It gives the time, the date...</i>

259
00:16:25,818 --> 00:16:28,446
<i>... and with a push of a button,</i>
